race.comment: DISCREETLY BLUE (4) returns and makes his stable debut for the Bain & Taylor camp. Looks to have come on nicely during the break, taking out his recent trial. Draws well for Holder and can make an immediate impact. ACT NATURAL (1) has been frustrating for punters, going under again as favourite just eight days ago. Is yet to miss the frame in all 12 career starts. Doesn't need to improve much to get the verdict. TIDDY WIDDY (11) is another that finds it hard to get off the mark but is knocking on the door. Likely to settle back early and be doing her best work late. JEWELS CAPTAIN (7) has returned with two solid efforts and should be hitting his straps now. Will just need some luck from the draw.
